cdata.name: HyperLending
cdata.desc:
HyperLending is a lending platform with cryptocurrencies as collateral for a convenient, safe and low-cost loan. The HyperLending platform is where the participants design the loan agreement principles and the lenders post the amount and term of the loan. 

HLD is an Ethereum-based ERC20 token to be a payment method for membership fees and management fees within the HyperLending ecosystem.
